name: Nothing is Lost
description:
I find things while creating.
While I disappear in forms and tunes.
Between Strokes in digital Worlds.
I create Space and breath Fresh Air, 
and although, I sometimes have to hit Home 
and face the facts… 
I know,
I can always return safely to my Crest.
Save in the Sacred flow between Heart & Head. 

Time is well spend 
When spend with you.

XXX
